<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="golden-adj">golden <strong><em>adj</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /'ɡəʊldən/    美 /'ɡoʊldən/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>金的；金 (黄) 色的；美好的；重要的：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>a golden crown
金皇冠</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>a <strong>golden</strong> saying / <strong>opportunity</strong>
金玉良言/绝好的机会</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>the golden rule
重要原则</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I think those <strong>golden days</strong> at school were the happiest of my life. 
我觉得上学的那段黄金岁月是我一生中最幸福的时光。</p><footer>译林⑥ – 2</footer></div></div>